snippet.title: Life Stories By Goalcast
snippet.description:
Life Stories will sweep you away on a journey with history’s most inspiring people.  

Join theses heroes who start from humble beginnings, do not let obstacles stop them from achieving their dreams and end up creating what the world believed to be impossible...

A refreshing new series of uplifting videos by Goalcast
